citation: Proclamation under the Tasmanian Health Organisations Act 2011 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Tasmanian Health Organisations Act 2011

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Tasmanian Health Organisations Act 2011 fix 1 July 2012 as the day on which commence the provisions of that Act that have not already commenced.

2 April 2012

PETER G. UNDERWOOD

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

MICHELLE O'BYRNE

Minister for Health

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 11 April 2012

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Health and Human Services.
